Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Every summer, millions of {\c&H8888FF&}people{\r} {\c&HDDDDDD&}experience{\r} the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.87,0:00:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}exact same betrayal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.87,0:00:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}You're at a party, a beach,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.93,0:00:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}a backyard barbecue.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.32,0:00:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}You take a big bite of {\c&HDDDDDD&}ice{\r} {\c&H8888FF&}cream{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.74,0:00:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}or a long sip of a frozen drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.51,0:00:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}And then your {\c&HFFDD44&}brain{\r} tries to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.94,0:00:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Why does eating something {\c&HDDDDDD&}cold{\r} hurt your HEAD?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.77,0:00:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}The {\c&HDDDDDD&}cold{\r} thing is in your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.42,0:00:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Your {\c&HFFDD44&}brain{\r} is encased in bone,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.41,0:00:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}insulated by fluid.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.02,0:00:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}How does {\c&HDDDDDD&}cold{\r} {\c&HDDDDDD&}ice{\r} {\c&H8888FF&}cream{\r} cause {\c&H8888FF&}pain{\r} in
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.55,0:00:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}your skull?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.76,0:00:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}It seems impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.89,0:00:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}The answer lies in your trigeminal nerve,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.72,0:00:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}the largest nerve in your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.70,0:00:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}This nerve controls facial sensation and is
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.02,0:00:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}directly connected to your palate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.06,0:00:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}When extreme {\c&HDDDDDD&}cold{\r} hits, the trigeminal nerve goes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.98,0:00:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}haywire.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.01,0:00:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\c&HDDDDDD&}Cold{\r} triggers your anterior cerebral artery to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.97,0:00:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}rapidly constrict, reducing blood flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.88,0:01:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Your body panics and {\c&H00F0FF&}immediately{\r} dilates the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.54,0:01:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}artery.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.43,0:01:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}This constriction-dilation cycle triggers nearby
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.09,0:01:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\c&H8888FF&}pain{\r} receptors.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.28,0:01:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Here's the wild part:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.79,0:01:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}your {\c&HFFDD44&}brain{\r} gets confused about WHERE the {\c&H8888FF&}pain{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.45,0:01:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}is coming from.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.55,0:01:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}The trigeminal nerve serves both your palate and
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.96,0:01:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}your forehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.03,0:01:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}So {\c&H8888FF&}pain{\r} signals from your mouth get
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.84,0:01:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}misinterpreted as coming from your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.62,0:01:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Press your tongue flat against the roof of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.56,0:01:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.34,0:01:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}The warmth from your tongue warms the palate,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.63,0:01:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}telling your blood vessels to stabilize.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.20,0:01:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\c&H8888FF&}Pain{\r} relief is almost instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.27,0:01:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Prevention is even better.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.78,0:01:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Eat {\c&HDDDDDD&}cold{\r} things slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.09,0:01:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Let them warm slightly in the front of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.23,0:01:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}your mouth before swallowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.88,0:01:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Your blood vessels will thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.24,0:01:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\c&HFFDD44&}Brain{\r} {\c&H00F0FF&}freeze{\r} isn't just a party trick topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.95,0:01:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Researchers use it to study migraines,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.71,0:01:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}vascular headaches, and {\c&H8888FF&}pain{\r} perception.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.34,0:01:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Your frozen drink mishap is actually contributing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.85,0:02:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}to medical {\c&H37AFD4&}science.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.24,0:02:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}So to recap: {\c&HDDDDDD&}Cold{\r} hits palate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.06,0:02:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Blood vessels freak out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.63,0:02:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Trigeminal nerve misfires.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.96,0:02:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}{\c&HFFDD44&}Brain{\r} thinks head is in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.93,0:02:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}You feel {\c&H8888FF&}pain.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.58,0:02:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Warm tongue fixes it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.57,0:02:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Simple!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.63,0:02:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Next time {\c&HFFDD44&}brain{\r} {\c&H00F0FF&}freeze{\r} hits,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.12,0:02:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}don't curse your {\c&HDDDDDD&}ice{\r} {\c&H8888FF&}cream.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.86,0:02:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Marvel at the complex neuroscience happening in
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.43,0:02:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}real-time inside your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.74,0:02:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Then press your tongue up,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.32,0:02:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}fix it in seconds, and keep eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.07,0:02:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Because {\c&H37AFD4&}science.{\r}